WEBVTT

00:12:27.080 --> 00:12:30.616
and every level of government
becomes radically more responsive

00:12:30.640 --> 00:12:31.920
to all the people.

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:35.800
What would it take
to mobilize 100 percent?

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:39.016
Well, we do have to push back
against efforts afoot

00:12:39.040 --> 00:12:40.776
all across the country right now

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:42.000
to make voting harder.

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:43.976
But at the same time,

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:47.136
we have to actively create
a positive culture of voting

00:12:47.160 --> 00:12:48.776
that people want to belong to,

00:12:48.800 --> 00:12:51.336
be part of, and experience together.

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:52.976
We have to make purpose.

00:12:53.000 --> 00:12:54.320
We have to make joy.

00:12:55.160 --> 00:12:57.816
So yes, let's have that revolution,

00:12:57.840 --> 00:13:00.336
a revolution of spirit, of ideas,